text: My cat pees in the toilet! I had a roommate be like ummmmmm so sometimes you don't flush? And I was all.... was there toilet paper? And he was like oh, come to think of it no? And this is how I figured out that potty training didn't fail and sometimes he wants to use the litter and sometimes the toilet's fine lol
NTA and I really want to see the dress
.... he went to the hospital and didn’t die, right?
